    <thetext>TaskListFilteredTree contains the UI needed for a basic task list without task focus and other things contributed by TaskListView, but it is hard to use it outside of TaskListView because TaskListView contains the logic for refreshing the tree and TaskListContentProvider depends on TaskListView. To allow easier reuse of TaskListFilteredTree we should decouple the refresh logic and content provider from the view.</thetext>
